        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> January 1, 2024</p>
        <br>
        <p>TechSolve Pro is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard information you provide when using our website and services.</p>
        <br>
        <h3 style="color:var(--primary-900);margin-bottom:12px">Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly, such as your name, email, phone number, and company when you fill out contact or inquiry forms. We also collect non-personally-identifiable information including browser type, pages visited, and time spent on our site through standard analytics tools.</p>
        <br>
        <h3 style="color:var(--primary-900);margin-bottom:12px">How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p>Information is used to respond to your inquiries, provide requested services, send updates relevant to your engagement with us, and improve our website. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
        <br>
        <h3 style="color:var(--primary-900);margin-bottom:12px">Contact</h3>
        <p>For privacy-related queries, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@techsolvepro.com" style="color:var(--primary-400)">privacy@techsolvepro.com</a></p>
    </div>
</section>
